Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 补给部搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是12mm法兰管件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱要的是10mm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<黑耀>上能用 但银色歼灭者用不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也不能怪他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10mm很少有人用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算想提意见 队长和铃城小姐也都不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥这会儿还被叫去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是法兰管件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试作机型就这点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺乏可维护性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也常听人这样说 真差这么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以说中看不中用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是高端新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有量产机完全没法比的大量专用配件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不能用其他曳战者的配件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟外观就跟其他机体不同啊 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用时留点神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然关键时刻掉链子就没你的戏唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你看它的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用了散热和减震的双重构造
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很优雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战场上需要的 可不是妇孺的优雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是爷们的蛮勇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 班长又性别歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 有空动嘴不如多动手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说 法兰管件怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是老婆 不能离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不合适的只能强扭它合适
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于闪击战失败
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈尔米亚战力被迫分为南北两部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰达斯军随一时后撤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却趁因戈尔米亚行军减缓之际 调整了态势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正伺机反攻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各地虽小规模战斗不断 却没有大规模进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样过了些时日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独立第八部队转战各地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今在威修佩地区 稍事休养
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(980,575)}不在之终
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 天堂 天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在澡堂说{\rsymbol2}「{\r}天堂天堂{\rsymbol2}」{\r}的 现实中还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是奶奶带大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还好威修佩有温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑溜溜的皮肤就近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托也为我这只能看见爷们屁股的人着想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开 在哪 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺行啊 你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊来啊 抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男浴池吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个混蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑 别跑 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对面不可能看得到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂偶像怎么能为这点事害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋名小姐 你是偶像?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坯子而已 还是落选的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 都试唱过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便唱两句
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要买的 就这些了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 这不是尾久井家的小伙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 好久不见了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 嘛 还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 小伙子 最近还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是{\rsymbol}…{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同队的越川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙他照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子参军之后 一次都没回来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔过来露个脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等有时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 好稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是威修佩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥都没有的落后小镇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不碰上熟人都难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候在这镇子 我每天都想离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在看还成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是{\rsymbol}…{\r}篠井老太婆?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没断气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那么容易死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你居然没被枪子儿打得稀巴烂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭老太婆都没断气 我怎么可能死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窗帘 拉开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多灰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸妈早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我偶尔回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始加压
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不算完美 但应该能撑到下次补给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,设备识别和磨合你来搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 为什么这全涂黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这些是第二整备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二整备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现场能完成的叫第一整备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其余的 要送到工厂才能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是试作品 里面满是柯贝尔尼斯工业的企业机密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做第一整备的地方很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家忙整备时你去泡温泉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泡得好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想泡温泉就快干活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温泉温泉 赶紧搞定这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 快点动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温泉温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是第八部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈尔米亚穿过塔斯卡冲这边来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办 队长不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯卡陷落看来是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今左文字队长和铃城曹长不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥权落在谷田军曹身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田军曹吃鱼中毒正在蹲厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为生吃了河里钓的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然谷田军曹身体不适{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道要曳战者机师来指挥?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦哟 我可不干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 轮到尾久井或辔田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找熟悉本地地理的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熟悉地理{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吗{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 赶紧搬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 请尽量拖延时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱的家伙可没多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寺井 申请援军了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,申请了 但总部也正头疼如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过塔斯卡的是一个师团
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久后 至少会有三个大队向这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,优先让平民去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成后 开始反击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班长做好炸桥准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 你们几个无论如何 也要把银色歼灭者准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人过一阵才会抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必惊慌 完全来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静转移
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想死在这镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死时的样子 可没人想看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇子我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是席加 敌人接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已确认12台曳战者 这就发图像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇民避难如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人进军比预想快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 再没多久威修佩就会进入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-10配件给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是暴风雨前的那玩意?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了沉默啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿你就觉得安静是福了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿 千万别挨敌人枪子儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏这会儿食物中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别停 径直去桥那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 冷静转移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是席加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方曳战者开始入侵城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 守住位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 然后去向面包店那个转角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面包店?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扳手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这边还在用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没见到敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说尾久井 指挥拜托给点力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边右转{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}不对 左转
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边是山並 现在敌人到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人{\rsymbol}…{\r}敌人到这个{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消灭一台曳战者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 没人掩护吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别一下都来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你是指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字队长平时都在做这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不承认被压制了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到处是敌人 该往哪打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 镇民避难马上完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 马上要起雾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雾?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节 会有很浓的河雾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起雾{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是一流的援军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雾哪能说{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起就起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这是搞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起雾倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可这下 不好打了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 镇民避难完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇民全员过桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员 开始反击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么反击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军已经太深入了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说这雾啥都看不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾久井 银色歼灭者还没动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太悬了啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人后续部队 确认20台曳战者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转轮旋转 目测稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,油压稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辅助系统的SP值 进不到正常范围
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者 装置 唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系统启动流程 运行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转写 吉米·哈兹福特 接入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾久井 开车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班长 这边好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗 过桥后立刻动手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是{\rsymbol}…{\r}时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
