Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:31.42,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.93,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:38.74,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… あの火は仲間か?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:43.49,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:48.98,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:52.86,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:58.67,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:03.81,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:09.06,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:13.63,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:14.88,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(640,660)}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:19.26,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:25.89,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.44,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…かかって来い{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:35.20,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.94,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.70,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.86,0:02:18.04,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}总有一天 向着这无望的高空
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.04,0:02:22.66,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志将一飞冲天
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.93,0:02:38.74,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是战友吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.00,0:02:43.49,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}当走之路是黑暗吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.09,0:02:48.98,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 在面前寒光闪动
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.13,0:02:52.86,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无名感情在胸中翻涌
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.05,0:02:58.67,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-此时此刻在此地 尚不能结束-
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.67,0:03:03.81,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那么就做好活下去的准备吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.93,0:03:09.06,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一腔热忱 越积越高无处释放
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.06,0:03:13.63,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这份量 怎可能不沉重{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.01,0:03:19.26,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}战场之上 笑谈青涩有何不可
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.26,0:03:25.89,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我会一个一个亲自去实践
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.44,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…放马过来{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:28.52,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}見渡す世界 足はすくむけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.38,0:22:32.39,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}歩みを止めぬビリーバー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:37.06,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}幾度の傷 痛みの中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:42.29,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一筋の強き意思見つける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:47.14,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}戸惑いに揺れる心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:52.08,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}足取りは覚束なくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:54.68,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}恐れはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:23:00.29,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}希望へと両手伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:05.60,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}通り抜ける 願い纏う風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:10.82,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}迷わない瞳はただ前を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:16.29,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}共に行けば 絶望など他愛ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:21.35,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重い闇さえ 振り払うだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:25.88,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸を震わせる未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:28.24,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}誓って
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.25,0:22:28.52,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}放眼整个世界 即便双脚在颤抖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.38,0:22:32.39,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸怀信念之人也不会停下脚步
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.66,0:22:37.06,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无数次受伤 无数次疼痛中
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.06,0:22:42.29,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那股强韧的意志映入眼帘
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.37,0:22:47.14,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}迷惑中动摇的心
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.57,0:22:52.08,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}即便步履已经蹒跚
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.44,0:22:54.68,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}也绝不畏惧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.01,0:23:00.29,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}向着希望 努力伸出双手
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.86,0:23:05.60,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}清风吹过 带来一份祈愿
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.70,0:23:10.82,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}坚定不移的瞳孔 只看前路
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.25,0:23:16.29,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}与你同行 绝望又算得上什么
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.45,0:23:21.35,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}再沉重的黑暗 也能一挥而散
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.62,0:23:25.88,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未来必定振奋人心
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.88,0:23:28.24,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我保证
